title: Top Ten Underrated AHS Characters
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I would absolutely love it if AHS gave us an in-depth Scathach backstory!
My favorite underrated character is lee Harris from Roanoke. I love how Ryan Murphy explored the lengths a mother will go to to protect her child.
Nan would have to be my favorite underrated character

I like Mallory. She's not super duper boom boom powerful. To me, if the writers gave more attention to the characters we'd see a more morose and melancholy Mallory. To me she gives me a very gloomy and kind of sad vibe. Mixed with her power and her loyalty to the coven just makes her such an interesting and amazing character that I think id just visually stunning.
When is beyond the horror episode 2 coming out/airing?
